<p>&#8216;Sanctioned Russian oligarchs from Vladimir Putin&#8217;s inner circle exploited a UK secrecy loophole left open by the government. Arkady and Boris Rotenberg &#8211; judo partners of the Russian president &#8211; used a type of company that was not required to identify its real owners.&#8217;</p>
